Bill of Materials for Version 1
(Amazon references aren't what I used, just a convenient reference)

Boards
Arduino Mega 2560 or clone (Mine came from Microcenter for $20)
https://www.amazon.com/ELEGOO-Compatible-Arduino-Projects-Compliant/dp/B01H4ZLZLQ

RAMPS 1.6 board (the 1.6 has better power electronics arrangements)
https://www.amazon.com/SIUKE-Heatsink-Expansion-Mainboard-Accessories/dp/B0CS6PJ69F

Connectors

Peltier - JST VL (Digi-Key)
Shell VLR-02V  (Digi-Key 455-2355-ND)
Pins SVF-42T-P2.0  (Digi Key 455-2347-1-ND)

